WEBVTT

00:03:57.840 --> 00:04:00.976
bunday istakdan mahrum 
shaxslarni o'rganish

00:04:01.000 --> 00:04:03.120
psixopatlar ayni shu toifa shaxslaridir.

00:04:04.200 --> 00:04:06.576
Psixopatiya nasldan-naslga o’tuvchi,

00:04:06.600 --> 00:04:08.696
rivojlanishdagi nuqson bo’lib,

00:04:08.720 --> 00:04:11.616
sovuqqon va bag'ritosh shaxsiyat,

00:04:11.640 --> 00:04:15.164
ba'zida o'ta tajovuzkorlikka moyillikdir.

00:04:16.040 --> 00:04:19.296
Ruhiy salomatlik institutida 
hamkasblarim bilan psixopat

00:04:19.320 --> 00:04:21.935
o’smirlarda miya skanerlari 
tadqiqotini olib bordik

00:04:21.959 --> 00:04:24.096
va bizning xulosalarimiz

00:04:24.120 --> 00:04:26.976
va bu boradagi boshqa tadqiqotlar xulosasi

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:29.296
psixopatlarda ayni uch xususiyatning

00:04:29.320 --> 00:04:32.240
mavjudligiga ishora qilmoqda.